VERSA SPECIFICATION NOTICE:

The VERSA (Vendor-neutral Extensible Repo Spec for Agents) specification defined in this 
repository is freely available for implementation by any individual or organization. 

Implementations of this specification in software may use any license, but attribution 
to the VERSA specification and its author (Alphin Tom) is required when referencing or 
documenting compliance with this specification.

